{"Title": "Computation offloading with ICN", "Year": 2018, "Source": "ICN - Proc. ACM Conf. Inf.-Cent. Netw.", "Volume": null, "Issue": null, "Art.No": null, "PageStart": 220, "PageEnd": 221, "CitedBy": 1, "DOI": "10.1145/3267955.3269009", "Link": "https://www.scopus.com/inward/record.uri?partnerID=HzOxMe3b&scp=85065909870&origin=inward", "Abstract": "\u00a9 2018 Copyright held by the owner/author(s).This demo shows an implementation of a computation-centric architecture over NDN. The system is able to perform in-network load balancing of incoming computation requests, reliably authenticate consumers and allow them to submit large payloads without routable prefixes. The system is able to migrate requested function in a form of unikernels where they are needed, follows ICN pull-based model and introduces only minimal changes to the NDN stack.", "AuthorKeywords": ["In-network processing", "Information Centric Networks", "Named Data Networking", "Naming", "Thunks"], "IndexKeywords": ["In-network processing", "Information Centric Networks", "Named data networkings", "Naming", "Thunks"], "DocumentType": "Conference Proceeding", "PublicationStage": null, "OpenAccess": 2, "EID": "2-s2.0-85065909870", "SubjectAreas": [["Information Systems", "COMP", "1710"], ["Computer Networks and Communications", "COMP", "1705"], ["Computer Science Applications", "COMP", "1706"]], "AuthorData": {"57206464172": {"Name": "Kr\u00f3l M.", "AuthorID": "57206464172", "AffiliationID": "60022148", "AffiliationName": "UCL"}, "57208837959": {"Name": "Nicolaescu A.C.", "AuthorID": "57208837959", "AffiliationID": "60022148", "AffiliationName": "UCL"}, "17435754200": {"Name": "Re\u00f1\u00e9 S.", "AuthorID": "17435754200", "AffiliationID": "60022148", "AffiliationName": "UCL"}, "25926838500": {"Name": "Ascigil O.", "AuthorID": "25926838500", "AffiliationID": "60022148", "AffiliationName": "UCL"}, "16048105300": {"Name": "Psaras I.", "AuthorID": "16048105300", "AffiliationID": "60022148", "AffiliationN